node.text: Great food 👏
That looks good! ❤️

It has been a while since we @WaaCowSG. Wife ordered this coz she has been thinking about it for a while. Today is also a day of non stop online meetings for all at home (except the kid), so can’t cook.

Can’t beat eating at location, after the meats are flamed, but that will be a few more weeks. So it’s food delivery for the time being.

We realised the kid don’t like eating it. So I ate 1.5 portions! 😂
